Job Responsibilities:

Website and mobile app user interface designs;
Produce all kind of graphic and digital design for banner and other presentation materials;
Work with project and development team; and
Manage any ad-hoc tasks or projects as assigned.

Job Requirements:

Higher Diploma or above in digital design, multimedia design, graphic communications or related field;
Minimum 3-4 years' of working experience in design related field, preferable with exposure in mobile / web product / financial or banking products;
Hands on skills in Adobe Photoshop, Illustrator, Sketch;
Knowledge of UI design principles and techniques;
Detail minded with can-do attitude and ability to multitask;
High level of initiative and ability to work under tight deadlines in a fast-paced, team-oriented environment; and
Provide online portfolio link in addition to resume.

To cope with our continuous growth and business expansion, we are looking for energetic and high calibre of candidates to join. 

Duties:


Responsible for user interface design of system, mobile apps and websites
Banner, image retouch and other graphics design


Requirements:


Diploma holder or above in Web / Multimedia / Graphics design or related discipline;
At least 3 years’ solid experience in Web/App/Multimedia design;
Proficiency in graphics & web design tools such as Adobe Photoshop,  Illustrator, XD or Sketch;
Knowledge of design, prototyping tools and usability best practices in wire frames and prototypes;
Strong sense on responsive design, UI/UX and technology trends;
Knowledge of iOS & Android app official UI guideline;
Knowledge of JavaScript, HTML5, CSS3 is a plus;
Responsible, detail-minded, have good interpersonal and communication skills;
Immediately available is preferable;
Candidates with more experience will be considered as Senior UX/UI Designer

At least 3 portfolios provided for review is a must

Interested parties, please send full resume with CURRENT & EXPECTED SALARY to Centaline Data Technology Limited.

Job Responsibilities
- Responsible for UI and UX design for applications including mobile apps, responsive website, console/dashboard.
- Contribute new ideas, translate concepts into user-friendly design.
- Identify and troubleshoot UX problems;
- Create user flow with details of all possible user scenarios;
- Follow up the development schedule with Project Manager and Developers;
- Work with Development Team and Designers to deliver the best UX and beautiful UI.
- Create pixel detailed graphics such as icons, banners, gif animation etc;
- Prepare necessary graphic materials for marketing purpose;
    
Job Requirements
- Higher Diploma, Associate Degree or Bachelor Degree Holder;
- Proficient in design software like Adobe Photoshop, XD/Sketch, Illustrator;
- At least 2-3 years of experience in UI and graphic design;
- Responsible, Self-starter, Attention to details, Independent and Well-Organized Team Player;
- Knowledge in HTML, CSS, Javascript is an advantage;
- Experience in video editing or motion graphics is an advantage;
- Good command of written and spoken English and Cantonese

You will enjoy our attractive benefits:

Competitive remuneration package 
Performance Bonus 
Medical Insurance 
5-day work per week 
Flexi-working hour 
General Holiday, Annual Leave, Family Care Leave and Anniversary Leave 
Casual wear in office 
Friendly working environment

The Job

Act as both front-end and back-end developer to cooperate with designers and other stakeholders to design, implement, test and document the web based applications and services;
Develop trendy features and user interfaces from wireframe models;
Ensure the best performance and user experience of the application, e.g. UAT, bug fixing and web speed;
Provide technical support to users;
Take up projects and other duties as assigned by supervisor;
Engage in AI Project;

The Person

Bachelor Degree in Computer Science / Information Technology or related discipline;
1 year hands-on internship experience in web application development and/or project experience;
Solid knowledge in Java or PHP and REST API;
Database systems' knowledge in MySQL or MSSQL or Oracle;
Knowledge in Python, Tensorflow, AI, React / Angular, JavaScript, CSS and HTML is an advantage;
Experience in Python and machine learning programming languages is a plus;
Experience in common machine learning or deep learning model is a plus

Please send your application with full resume as well as portfolio stating your present and expected salary to the Company by clicking on the "Apply now". Please also quote the reference number of the applied position in the subject field.

ROLES & RESPONSIBILITIES:
Advise on the creation of UX/UI assets (sketches, user flows, wireframes & prototypes) based on limitations of tech stack
Track and perform analysis on business results, analytics, customer behavior, and campaign effectiveness
Responsible for product function design, write PRD and promote product development and testing online, and control the progress of product construction
Coordinate and participate in multifaceted projects – involving both internal and external parties. Resolving conflicting interests and competing priorities of different stakeholders
Analyse analytics, user feedback and research findings to refine design decisions and product strategies
Analyse user feedback and find research to refine design decisions and product strategies

SKILLS & EXPERIENCES REQUIRED

Diploma or degree in Graphic Design, UI/UX Design, Multimedia or related major;
3+ years of relevant experience as a Product Designer (UI/UX) for mobile and web customer facing products.
Experience with defining product requirements, tracking performance, exploring drivers, diagnosing issues, etc.
In-depth knowledge and experience of user interface design with SaaS products;
Ability to visualize and execute design concepts and ideas quickly, from ideation to prototyping, to user testing/validation, to execution;
Proficient in a variety of methods to convey ideas and concepts (e.g. storyboards, wireframes, prototypes, etc) to product owners and business stakeholders;
A portfolio that demonstrates an ability to turn ideas into a strong and unique creative vision. A portfolio that provides insights into the candidate’s design thinking process is a must;
Proficient with design and prototyping tools, i.e. Sketch, InVision, Zeplin, Overflow, Marvel, Framer, Figma, Adobe XD;
Excellent communication skills, cross-team collaboration skill and ability to make compelling and clear design presentations for varied audiences;
Good command of written & spoken English, Mandarin and Cantonese; 

BENEFIT 

5-days work
Bank Holiday
Free snack and drink
Happy team culture
Flexible work environment
Smart work from home
Medical insurance

Responsibilities:

Design user interface for Portal, POS, Customer Frontends (Mobile Apps, Tablet, PC);
Design for UI and UX;
Collaborate with our development team to bring your designs to live;
Communicate with clients to gather requirements and present design concept.

Requirements:

Degree Holder in digital design or related disciplines;
Minimum 2 year of UI /UX design experience (especially on web and Mobile App), or equivalent experience;
Experience designing intuitive user experiences based on requirements;
Proficiency in graphic design - familiar with Photoshop or AI;
Proficiency in prototyping tools like Sketch, Figma;
Passionate to provide innovative, creative and reliable digital business solutions (web, app, system) to our clients;
Good team player with strong growth mindset, excellent communication, work with strict deadlines and under high-pressure situations;
Good command of spoken and written English, Chinese and Mandarin;
Candidate with more experience will be considered as Senior UX/UI Designer;

Interested parties please submit your application to our mailbox by clicking Apply Now.

Personal data provided in the employment applications will be treated in strict confidence and used only for recruitment purpose.
